    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116230/extras/208bab76b859f1efe590a289684c6912.poster.avif?t=1771050864\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116230/extras/208bab76b859f1efe590a289684c6912.webm?t=1771050864\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116230/extras/208bab76b859f1efe590a289684c6912.mp4?t=1771050864\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Abashed》是一款2.5D叙事驱动的横版卷轴游戏，让你探索艾萨克（Issac）的生活——一个与精神病共存的男人。有一天，当他独自醒来时，踏上了寻找失踪伴侣真相的旅程。在这过程中，他必须直面自己最深的恐惧和最黑暗的秘密。加入艾萨克的旅程，体验一个关于爱、失落、恐惧和接纳的故事。现实并非表面看起来的那样。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >扭曲现实</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116230/extras/688a650b030ff22992a840ff3076f49f.poster.avif?t=1771050864\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116230/extras/688a650b030ff22992a840ff3076f49f.webm?t=1771050864\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116230/extras/688a650b030ff22992a840ff3076f49f.mp4?t=1771050864\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >服用冥想药物以改变现实，短暂改变周围的环境。利用这项能力解锁隐藏区域、寻找线索并解决谜题。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >解谜</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116230/extras/9371facf53a020f5cd7fc834fb8f40c4.poster.avif?t=1771050864\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116230/extras/9371facf53a020f5cd7fc834fb8f40c4.webm?t=1771050864\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116230/extras/9371facf53a020f5cd7fc834fb8f40c4.mp4?t=1771050864\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >体验独特的互联谜题，充分利用你的能力找到有趣的解决方案。操控周围环境，解锁隐藏的真相，深入探索未知世界。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >特色</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一个心理冒险的旅程，设定在艾萨克的内心世界中，现实与超现实的界限逐渐模糊。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >涉及改变现实、操控环境、寻找和使用道具的谜题。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >邂逅有趣的角色，每个角色都有独特的特征。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >深刻的叙事，探讨心理健康主题，情感丰富。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >沉浸在独特手工绘制的艺术风格和令人心悸的美丽环境中。</p></li></ul>",
